{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":416133,"duration_api_ms":390553,"num_turns":73,"result":"```json\n{\n  \"change_summary\": \"Restored token usage and cache efficiency metrics across all backends. Extended TokenCounts with cache_read_tokens and cache_creation_tokens fields. Added ClaudeUsage struct with serde aliases to parse Claude CLI envelope usage (input_tokens/tokens_in, output_tokens/tokens_out, cache_read_input_tokens/cached_in, cache_creation_input_tokens). Added extract_codex_usage_from_stdout() that scans NDJSON lines in reverse for the last usage event with cached_input_tokens. Extended OpenRouterUsage with cache_read_input_tokens, cache_creation_input_tokens, and prompt_tokens_details for OpenAI-style cached_tokens. Added structured tracing::info! event in service.rs after invocation metadata finalization with all token fields, presence booleans, and session_reused flag. Fixed stub_backend struct literal for new fields.\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Extended TokenCounts struct in model.rs with cache_read_tokens: Option<u32> and cache_creation_tokens: Option<u32>\",\n      \"order\": 1,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added ClaudeUsage struct with serde aliases (tokens_in, tokens_out, cached_in) and usage: Option<ClaudeUsage> field to ClaudeEnvelope in process_backend.rs\",\n      \"order\": 2,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Wired Claude envelope usage into TokenCounts in the Claude decoder path, replacing TokenCounts::default()\",\n      \"order\": 3,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added extract_codex_usage_from_stdout() function that scans NDJSON stdout in reverse for last usage event with input_tokens, output_tokens, cached_input_tokens\",\n      \"order\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Wired Codex usage extraction into the Codex decoder path, replacing TokenCounts::default()\",\n      \"order\": 5,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Extended OpenRouterUsage with cache_read_input_tokens, cache_creation_input_tokens, and PromptTokensDetails struct; mapped cache_read_tokens from Anthropic native or OpenAI prompt_tokens_details.cached_tokens\",\n      \"order\": 6,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Fixed stub_backend.rs struct literal to include cache_read_tokens: None, cache_creation_tokens: None\",\n      \"order\": 7,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added structured tracing::info! event in service.rs after metadata finalization with invocation_id, backend, model, attempt, duration_ms, prompt_tokens, completion_tokens, cache_read_tokens, cache_creation_tokens, tokens_reported, cache_reported, session_reused\",\n      \"order\": 8,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added unit tests: Claude envelope with usage, without usage (backward compat), with field aliases; Codex NDJSON extraction, empty stdout, last-event selection, skipping non-usage lines; OpenRouter Anthropic cache fields, OpenAI prompt_tokens_details, missing cache fields\",\n      \"order\": 9,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": [\n    \"cargo test: 667 passed, 0 failed, 0 ignored\",\n    \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings: clean, no warnings\",\n    \"cargo fmt --check: clean, no formatting issues\",\n    \"Claude envelope with usage test: validates input_tokens=100, output_tokens=50, cache_read_input_tokens=80, cache_creation_input_tokens=20\",\n    \"Claude envelope without usage test: validates backward compat deserialization with no usage field\",\n    \"Claude envelope alias test: validates tokens_in/tokens_out/cached_in aliases\",\n    \"Codex NDJSON extraction test: validates prompt=500, completion=120, total=620, cache_read=300 from turn.completed event\",\n    \"Codex empty stdout test: validates TokenCounts::default() returned\",\n    \"Codex last-event test: validates second usage event (600/200/400) picked over first (100/10/50)\",\n    \"OpenRouter Anthropic cache fields test: validates cache_read_input_tokens=80, cache_creation_input_tokens=20\",\n    \"OpenRouter OpenAI prompt_tokens_details test: validates cached_tokens=60 from nested details\",\n    \"OpenRouter missing cache fields test: validates backward compat with only standard 3 fields\"\n  ],\n  \"outstanding_risks\": [\n    \"Claude CLI envelope format assumption: if Claude CLI changes its usage field structure, the ClaudeUsage struct may need updating. Serde aliases provide some resilience.\",\n    \"Codex CLI NDJSON format assumption: the extraction scans for any JSON line with a 'usage' object. If Codex changes its event format, the scanner may need adjustment.\",\n    \"tracing::info! uses -1 sentinel for missing token counts; downstream log consumers must handle this convention.\"\n  ]\n}\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"8271ac28-e625-47c7-acf1-433129ad04f7","total_cost_usd":2.586347100000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":61,"cache_creation_input_tokens":62672,"cache_read_input_tokens":3251707,"output_tokens":17347,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":62672,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":61,"outputTokens":17347,"cacheReadInputTokens":3251707,"cacheCreationInputTokens":62672,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.4515335000000005,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":88,"outputTokens":5010,"cacheReadInputTokens":592431,"cacheCreationInputTokens":40346,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.13481359999999998,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_d